-- Avusa Full-Year Profit Falls 48% to $21 Million, Dividend Increases by 25%
-- Vernon Wessels
-- 2010-06-24T05:05:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-24/avusa-full-year-profit-falls-48-to-21-million-dividend-increases-by-25-.html

          
          
             Avusa Ltd. said net income in the
fiscal year through March 31 fell to 159 million rand from 308
million rand a year earlier.  
 The company declared a dividend of 75 cents for the year,
Avusa said in a statement published in the Business Day
newspaper.  
          
          


  


        